{"tid":996403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[環保撚末日] 派錢耗近500萬張紙 波叔準備下世做樹精","createTime":"2019-01-26T09:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T14:59:16.000Z","uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"faa7234e36b574c3f4c54981ba17b433aa46b833","tid":996403,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/287229/%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E8%9A%8A-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E8%80%97466%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E7%B4%99-%E7%96%8A%E5%9F%8B%E9%AB%98%E9%81%8Eifc-%E7%92%B0%E5%9C%98-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F287229%2F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A24000%25E8%259A%258A-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%2580%2597466%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E7%2596%258A%25E5%259F%258B%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2581%258Eifc-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%259C%2598-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%2581%25BD%25E9%259B%25A3%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=M3ZqFwR%2B202pwTicjjMYPjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=37ee0d62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/287229/%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E8%9A%8A-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E8%80%97466%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E7%B4%99-%E7%96%8A%E5%9F%8B%E9%AB%98%E9%81%8Eifc-%E7%92%B0%E5%9C%98-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府21日起派發「關愛共享計劃」4,000元的申請表格，當局不設網上申請安排，而是以傳統「遞紙」方式申請，首階段印製了100萬份中文版申請表格及33萬份英文版申請表格，結果即日派罄，其後加印100萬份中文版，共印製至少233萬份表格。<br />\n以每份4頁表格最少佔用兩張A4紙計算，即使未計各區議員及市民自行印刷的表格、證件副本等，是次派錢計劃已耗用近466萬張紙，全部疊起來可達512米高，相當於1.2棟國際金融中心(IFC)的高度、比484米的全港最高大廈環球貿易廣場（ICC）更高。<br />\n<br />\n有環保團體及立法會議員對情況感擔憂，形容是「樹的災難」，促請政府研究推動電子版「遞表」，避免「災難」重演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9aww0O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9aww0O.png&h=44fed339&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c31e3a2ff64d504ffd7076ea98b47a508c262062","tid":996403,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e314fa74226a3b57d9ce75286b4469e1acdfa72","tid":996403,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa424bb73185239cd033b9f65b6978e051435f7","tid":996403,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"要人要點將個波交畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}